name: Cultural
cityStateTypeUniques: Give +5 Culture Points to a civilization when that civilization is a Friend to the City-State. Give +10 Culture Points to a civilization when that civilization is an Ally to the City-State.

name: Maritime
cityStateTypeUniques: Give +1 Food or 1 Wood Boats unit to a civilization when that civilization is a Friend of the City-State. Give +2 Food or 2 Wood Boats units to a civilization when that civilization is an Ally to the City-State.
